    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, and the interior is spotless, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth-running engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. This car has been meticulously maintained and garaged its entire life, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants the very best.",
