    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This beauty has been incredibly reliable for me and still looks fantastic pulling into the driveway. It\u2019s in really solid shape and honestly drives like a total dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. I\u2019ve truly loved owning this one, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions at all; I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 29900.0,
