      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, high-performing daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor signs of road use consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation system and premium audio\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that runs quietly and efficiently. It comes with a complete folder of service records, including a recent professional inspection and oil change. This is a well-cared-for example that balances luxury and longevity, perfect for a buyer who values both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34500.0,
